									</a>
		
									<div class="accordion-content">
										<p>Cyber-attacks cost a fortune. According to the report published by Kaspersky Lab, the average cost of a data breach for a small firm in 2017 was $117,000, which is not a small amount!</br>
Small firms need to be very careful and protect themselves from such attacks to save up for future.</br>
You may not have the means to hire a group of employees to oversee your firm’s cyber defense, but this is where the role and utility of a cybersecurity consultant comes into the equation. The consultant comes up with a software that helps a company keep their data secure and avoid costly data breaches.</p>
									</div>
								</li>
		
								<li class="accordion-item">
